  <section class="card" style="margin-top:18px">
    <h3>Mini Playbook</h3>
    <p><strong>Design for autonomy</strong> (offer rationale, choice, competence-building feedback). Pair <strong>specific, challenging goals</strong> with <strong>if-then plans</strong>. Raise <strong>self-efficacy</strong> via mastery steps and credible feedback. Choose rewards that are <em>informational</em> (signal progress/competence) rather than controlling. Use the <strong>BCT Taxonomy</strong> to mix techniques deliberately.</p>
  </section>

